snippet: Andy Murray outgunned Bulgaria's Grigor Dimitrov 6-4 7-6(2) in the final of the China Open on Sunday to claim his 40th career title and continue his pursuit of the world number one spot....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray outgunned Bulgaria's Grigor Dimitrov 6-4 7-6(2) in the final of the China Open on Sunday to claim his 40th career title and continue his pursuit of the world number one spot.

headline.print_headline: Murray Battles Past Dimitrov to Clinch China Open Title
headline.main: Murray Battles Past Dimitrov to Clinch China Open Title
